## Adventurer Trainer
I have now broken into about 20 different games, using different techniques for each of them, but there is one that I must say, is amazing, adventurer Trainer 0.2.3b, is without a doubt, the only game I have no way to crack. The creator compiled a single file that they do not wish to be read, which is about 17 lines long. No modern decompiler can accurately bypass what the creator did to compile their code. If you decompile and run it, it crashes. You try to bypass it, it crashes. You create an redirect path, it crashes, you even try to hex edit, it won't work. Grep won't help nor does find. I can't crack it, just wow. Had to write this just to congrulate how well done it is. Some games try to use username checks for their patreon users to see if they are allowed to cheat or not or use simple boolean, this is without a doubt the best work I've seen on Itch.io so far.
